                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17701024-55-victim471 t17701024-55-viclabel258"></join>, by beating and forcing his head against the waistcoat of his school-room, on the <rs id="t17701024-55-cd259" type="crimeDate">8th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17701024-55-off257 t17701024-55-cd259"></join>, where by he received on the right side of his head, above the right ear, a mortal structure, of which he languished from the 8th till the 9th of October, and then died
            </rs>. He stood charged on the coroner's inquisition for manslaughter. *</p>
               <p>
            
